4150   // (early.exiting.I) from the exit block (ir-bb<exit.I>) and route through a
4151   // new vector.early.exit block. Update ir-bb<exit.I>'s phis to extract their
4152   // values at the first active lane:
4153   //
4154   // Input:
4155   //  early.exiting.I:
4156   //     ...
4157   //    EMIT branch-on-cond vp<%cond.I>
4158   //  Successor(s): in.loop.succ, ir-bb<exit.I>
4159   //
4160   //  ir-bb<exit.I>:
4161   //    IR %phi = phi [ vp<%incoming.I>, early.exiting.I ], ...
4162   //
4163   // Output:
4164   //  early.exiting.I:
4165   //    ...
4166   //  Successor(s): in.loop.succ
4167   //
4168   //  vector.early.exit.I:
4169   //    EMIT vp<%exit.val> = extract-lane vp<%first.lane>, vp<%incoming.I>
4170   //  Successor(s): ir-bb<exit.I>
4171   //
4172   //  ir-bb<exit.I>:
4173   //    IR %phi = phi ... (extra operand: vp<%exit.val> from
4174   //                                      vector.early.exit.I)
4175   //
4176   for (auto [Exit, VectorEarlyExitVPBB] :
